		<title>Profesor Potočnjak upozorio na zamke i probleme oko nacionalne mirovine</title>
		<link>https://www.mirovina.hr/novosti/profesor-potocnjak-upozorio-na-zamke-i-probleme-oko-nacionalne-mirovine/</link>
		<comments>https://www.mirovina.hr/novosti/profesor-potocnjak-upozorio-na-zamke-i-probleme-oko-nacionalne-mirovine/#respond</comments>
		<pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2019 10:39:26 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Josip Mihaljević]]></dc:creator>
