				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<h3>&#8220;Medicinsko čudo&#8221;, &#8220;najstarija majka na svijetu&#8221; samo su neki od opisa za slučaj iz Indije, gdje je žena u 73. godini pomoću carskog reza rodila dvije blizankinje.</h3>
<div id="attachment_27574" style="max-width: 1290px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img data-attachment-id="27574" data-permalink="https://www.mirovina.hr/novosti/medicinsko-cudo-indijka-u-73-godini-zivota-rodila-zdrave-blizankinje/attachment/pixa-8/" data-orig-file="https://i0.wp.com/www.mirovina.hr/app/uploads/2019/09/pixa.jpg?fit=1280%2C849&amp;ssl=1" data-orig-size="1280,849" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;5&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Canon EOS 5D Mark III&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;44&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;100&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.025&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="pixa" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://i0.wp.com/www.mirovina.hr/app/uploads/2019/09/pixa.jpg?fit=400%2C265&amp;ssl=1" data-large-file="https://i0.wp.com/www.mirovina.hr/app/uploads/2019/09/pixa.jpg?fit=1024%2C679&amp;ssl=1" class="size-full wp-image-27574" src="https://i0.wp.com/www.mirovina.hr/app/uploads/2019/09/pixa.jpg?resize=1280%2C849&#038;ssl=1" alt="" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/www.mirovina.hr/app/uploads/2019/09/pixa.jpg?w=1280&amp;ssl=1 1280w, https://i0.wp.com/www.mirovina.hr/app/uploads/2019/09/pixa.jpg?resize=400%2C265&amp;ssl=1 400w, https://i0.wp.com/www.mirovina.hr/app/uploads/2019/09/pixa.jpg?resize=768%2C509&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.mirovina.hr/app/uploads/2019/09/pixa.jpg?resize=1024%2C679&amp;ssl=1 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" data-recalc-dims="1" /><p class="wp-caption-text">Foto: Pixabay</p></div>
<p>Žena iz Indije za koju službeni dokumenti pokazuju da je rođena u srpnju 1946.  godine upravo je rodila dvije blizankinje, piše <a href="https://magazin.hrt.hr/540085/znanost-i-tehnologija/indijka-u-73-rodila-blizankinje" target="_blank" rel="noopener">magazin.hrt.hr</a>.</p>
<p>Liječnici su ocijenili da se radi o &#8220;medicinskom čudu i postignuću suvremene medicine.&#8221; Erramatti Mangayamma</p>
<div class="box related-post right">
                            <a href="https://www.mirovina.hr/novosti/foto-jeste-li-se-ikada-pitali-izgledaju-blizanci-kad-ostare/">
                                <div class="image"><img width="200" height="154" src="https://i0.wp.com/www.mirovina.hr/app/uploads/2018/11/blizanke-100.png?fit=200%2C154&amp;ssl=1" class="attachment-200x200 size-200x200 wp-post-image" alt="blizanke 100" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/www.mirovina.hr/app/uploads/2018/11/blizanke-100.png?w=755&amp;ssl=1 755w, https://i0.wp.com/www.mirovina.hr/app/uploads/2018/11/blizanke-100.png?resize=400%2C309&amp;ssl=1 400w" sizes="(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px" data-attachment-id="18302" data-permalink="https://www.mirovina.hr/novosti/foto-jeste-li-se-ikada-pitali-izgledaju-blizanci-kad-ostare/attachment/blizanke-100/" data-orig-file="https://i0.wp.com/www.mirovina.hr/app/uploads/2018/11/blizanke-100.png?fit=755%2C583&amp;ssl=1" data-orig-size="755,583" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="blizanke 100" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://i0.wp.com/www.mirovina.hr/app/uploads/2018/11/blizanke-100.png?fit=400%2C309&amp;ssl=1" data-large-file="https://i0.wp.com/www.mirovina.hr/app/uploads/2018/11/blizanke-100.png?fit=755%2C583&amp;ssl=1" /></div>
                                <p>[FOTO] Jeste li se ikada pitali kako izgledaju blizanci kad ostare?</p>
                            </a>
                        </div>
<p>začela je umjetnom oplodnjom, jer u 57 godina braka sa svojim mužem Sitharamom Rajaraom nikako nije mogla ostati trudna prirodnim putem.</p>
<p>Tim od 10 liječnika brinuo je o njenoj trudnoći i porodu:</p>
<blockquote><p>&#8220;To je medicinsko čudo i postignuće suvremene medicine. Također, začeće in-vitro (IVF) ne ovisi samo o znanosti, važna je i milost božja&#8221;, kazao je glavni liječnik.</p></blockquote>
<p>Majka je rodila carskim rezom, a obje bebe su zdrave. Čudo!</p>
